06/11/76  Master Directories

Master directories:
  are created using the -logical_volume control argument to the create_dir
command;
  are listed by name in the registration record for the logical volume;
  possess attributes like other directories;
  draw quota from master directory quota account maintained in the logical
volume registration record;
  can only be created if the user has a quota account on the logical volume
with enough unallocated quota to satisfy the request.
